{"tid":200481,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日午餐 香菇肉餅飯","createTime":"2017-04-14T03:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T06:49:11.000Z","uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"678e0dfe72e505e90f02a7b842a23245ee9de82a","tid":200481,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/14/115716_db4a320f2e672ea9d059fdc679fd71b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F14%2F115716_db4a320f2e672ea9d059fdc679fd71b4.jpg&h=19d1c13c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cbc50447920641e37fb1e4466efb41d6b633b20","tid":200481,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:01:25.000Z","msg":"之前食開佢個隻蔥油肉餅飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係已經無再出,宜家得返呢隻<br />\n<br />\n無蔥油,同埋肉餅入面好乾,同之前個隻差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好彩佢話今日係復活節,叫飯餐送多一隻蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我有2隻蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將蛋汁加埋肉餅入面一齊食又係另一種滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原價39,有VIP卡,33蚊,抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f468c79ddee3a7e943c6d647339b293a54c2b4","tid":200481,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f190d19d15a4a4f8d98458b06d7b430d56fc5d","tid":200481,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1beef70646379f8fb07af27da93ef211000e6709","tid":200481,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"點解隻碟有咁多水嘅 <img